===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*h₂yew-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|abjuren}}, from {{der|en|la|abiūrō|t=deny upon oath}} (possibly via {{der|en|frm|abiurer|abjurer}}), formed from {{m|la|ab|t=from, away from}} + {{m|la|iūro|t=swear or take an oath}}, from {{m|la|iūs|t=law, right, duty}}.<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=3}}</ref>

